cinnamon.engine.utils

Class SphereBounds

  • java.lang.Object
    • cinnamon.engine.utils.Bounds
      • cinnamon.engine.utils.SphereBounds
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Position, Size
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MutableSphereBounds

    public abstract class SphereBounds
extends Bounds

    Implementation of Bounds whose containment and intersection tests have been overridden to perform against a sphere instead of the implicit box defined by Bounds.
